{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "771a40cc-075d-4acc-ba2d-46646d5183cb", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/771a40cc-075d-4acc-ba2d-46646d5183cb@2.pkg/1772602441028/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602441771", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/771a40cc-075d-4acc-ba2d-46646d5183cb@2.pkg/1772602441028/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602441771"}, "identifier": "771a40cc-075d-4acc-ba2d-46646d5183cb", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>《陋室铭》表达了作者安贫乐道、淡泊名利的情感。A.体现了陶渊明的悠然闲适；B项体现了安于简朴的生活，以遵循道义为乐；D.体现了诸葛亮的淡泊宁静，均与《陋室铭》情感一致。C.“最爱湖东行不足，绿杨阴里白沙堤”表达的是白居易对于西湖早春景色的喜爱和赞美，与《陋室铭》情感不一致。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列诗句与《陋室铭》中作者表达的情感不一致的是（ &nbsp;）</span></p>\n</div>\n", "label": "", "title": "下列诗句与《陋室铭》中作者表达的情感不一致的是（  ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/771a40cc-075d-4acc-ba2d-46646d5183cb@2.pkg/item.json?v=1752735930600", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>采菊东篱下，悠然见南山（陶渊明《饮酒》）</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">“饭疏食，饮水，曲肱而枕之，乐亦在其中矣。不义而富且贵，于我如浮云。” （孔子《论语·述而》）​</p>\n</div>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>会当凌绝顶，一览众山小（杜甫《望岳》）</span></p>\n</div>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>非淡泊无以明志，非宁静无以致远（诸葛亮《诫子书》）</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列诗句与《陋室铭》中作者表达的情感不一致的是（ &nbsp;）</span></p>\n</div>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "5136342961", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342961", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "771a40cc-075d-4acc-ba2d-46646d5183cb", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列诗句与《陋室铭》中作者表达的